PN,41801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,FThe brutal killings of two pensioners
OL,8,Fin their home by a mental health
OL,9,Fpatient who had just walked out of
OL,10,Fhospital had major rammifications for
OL,11,Fthe authorities in Northern Ireland.
OL,13,FMichael and Majorie Cawdery were
OL,14,Fstabbed to death in their Co Armagh
OL,15,Fhome at the hands of a paranoid
OL,16,Fschizophrenic.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,FOn Thursday, a revised Code of
OL,8,FPractice to the Mental Health
OL,9,F(Northern Ireland) Order 1986 to drive
OL,10,F"improvements in care, safety and
OL,11,Faccountability" was launched.
OL,13,FHowever, that was overshadowed by a
OL,14,Frow between a grieving relative who
OL,15,Fplayed a key role in bringing about
OL,16,Fsome of the major changes, and the
OL,17,FDepartment of Health.
OL,19,FThe Cawdery's son-in-law believes they
OL,20,Ftried to censor him for the length of
OL,21,Ftime it has taken.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,FCharles Little said: "It was my family
OL,8,Fwho were killed on that day. This is
OL,9,Fabout making changes to prevent what
OL,10,Fhappened to my family happening to
OL,11,Fanyone else. If I want to say what the
OL,12,Fcontext of that is, I have the right
OL,13,Fto say it.
OL,15,FThe Cawdery's were stabbed to death by
OL,16,FThomas McEntee at their home in
OL,17,FPortadown in May 2017.
OL,19,FThe judge described the attack as
OL,20,F"frenzied, horrific and sustained".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,FMcEntee was handed a life sentence
OL,8,Fwith an order to serve at least 10
OL,9,Fyears in jail, after admitting
OL,10,Fmanslaughter on the grounds of
OL,11,Fdiminished responsibility.
OL,13,FA coroner ruled the pensioner's deaths
OL,14,Fwere "entirely preventable".
OL,16,FThe health and justice departments at
OL,17,FStormont oversaw an update to the code
OL,18,Fwhich includes dedicated guidance for
OL,19,FHealth and Social Care Trusts, PSNI
OL,20,Fand NIAS to allow multi-agency working
OL,21,Fin supporting people in crisis.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,FIn his contribution to inform changes
OL,8,Fto the code through "real-world
OL,9,Fexperience" , Mr Little was asked to
OL,10,Fleave out an important point he wanted
OL,11,Fto make in a proposed joint press
OL,12,Frelease.
OL,14,FUTV obtained the chain of emails
OL,15,Fbetween Mr Little and the Department
OL,16,Fof Health.
OL,18,FMr Little's contribution said he
OL,19,Ffirmly believed the code of practice
OL,20,Fshould contribute significantly to
OL,21,Fpreventing these avoidable deaths.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,FHe wanted to include the line, "It has
OL,8,Ftaken an unacceptable nine years to
OL,9,Fget this final result," because of his
OL,10,Ffirm believe it should have been
OL,11,Fimplemented a long time ago.
OL,13,FCharles told UTV: "If they weren't
OL,14,Fgoing to say it took nine years to get
OL,15,Fhere, I was going to say it took nine
OL,16,Fyears to get here because that's the
OL,17,Ftruth. And if they want to be honest
OL,18,Fand open, if they want to have a duty
OL,19,Fof candor, then you've got to`you've
OL,20,Fgot to tell the truth".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,F"Lives been lost in that period, and
OL,8,Fsome of them are lives that perhaps
OL,9,Fcould have been saved by all this work
OL,10,Fthat's been launched today."
OL,12,FOn Monday, Charles received an email
OL,13,Ffrom the Department of Health which
OL,14,Fsaid his quotes had to be cut down but
OL,15,Fhe noticed the crucial line he wanted
OL,16,Fkept in was gone.
OL,18,FHe replied and said he was happy for
OL,19,Fhis words to be edited, but he put
OL,20,Fthat line back in, highlighted it in
OL,21,Fred, and insisted it had to be kept in.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,FHowever, the department responded
OL,8,Fwith, "The addition of the line in red
OL,9,Fwould be difficult for us, and it
OL,10,Fwould be probably best if we
OL,11,Frespectfully remove the quotation
OL,12,Fcompletely."
OL,14,FCharles withdrew his voice from the
OL,15,Fjoint public statement, but not from
OL,16,Fspeaking at the private launch of the
OL,17,Fcode on Thursday morning where he met
OL,18,Fwith Health Minister Mike Nesbitt.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,FMr Little said: "He and his staff will
OL,8,Fcome up with an initial plan as to how
OL,9,Fthey'll take this forward and get the
OL,10,Fother missing recommendations
OL,11,Fimplemented. So, there is some good
OL,12,Fcoming out of this."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,FIn a statement, the Department of
OL,8,FHealth said they "offered Mr Little
OL,9,Fthe opportunity to contribute a quote
OL,10,Fto its press release for the event and
OL,11,Fwhen he offered a very long statement
OL,12,Fan extract was suggested, which
OL,13,Fprovided balance and reflected his
OL,14,Fview that the Code is good but that
OL,15,Fthere is more to be done.
OL,17,F"The additional line seemed accusatory
OL,18,Fand inappropriate for inclusion in a
OL,19,FDepartmental press release.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,F"It is of course entirely appropriate
OL,8,Fthat Mr Little would release his own
OL,9,Fmore detailed statement which reflects
OL,10,Fhis position on the range of issues
OL,11,Femerging from the Cawdery Inquest, of
OL,12,Fwhich the Code addresses some," they
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,F"It is not unusual that an Inquest and
OL,16,Fthe recommendations from that process
OL,17,Fprovide the impetus to drive change,
OL,18,Fparticularly as the related SAI work
OL,19,Fwas still ongoing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783781278
OL,3,CRelative of elderly couple killed in
OL,4,CPortadown in row with Department of
OL,5,CHealth
OL,7,F"The work started approximately 2
OL,8,Fmonths after the Coroner's report was
OL,9,Fpublished in December 2023.
OL,11,F"It is very disappointing when Mr
OL,12,FLittle decides to strike out at
OL,13,Fofficials who have only ever been
OL,14,Fsupportive and who have strived to
OL,15,Ffacilitate resolution of his issues."
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
OL,20,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,21,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/12
